    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover Lost Magic</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work as an Archivist Wizard to secure locations and face waves of enemies. Unlock access to greater magic and craft and upgrade your spells to survive the horde.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create your own spells</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/43e6885c8916e4feccbf90fbbf9d5dab.poster.avif?t=1755691617\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/43e6885c8916e4feccbf90fbbf9d5dab.webm?t=1755691617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/43e6885c8916e4feccbf90fbbf9d5dab.mp4?t=1755691617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Features a voxel based spell crafting system with emergent elemental properties that determine the behavior of the spells. Learn how the elements interact to bend them to your will and craft your weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enhance your magic with powerful runes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Apply runes to your spells to modify and enhance them, Anchor runes to lock them in place and, beam runes to project energy, trigger runes to enable elements or even activate a nested spell</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/95a087c66e4da335130ad6f3d6f1a3d4.poster.avif?t=1755691617\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/95a087c66e4da335130ad6f3d6f1a3d4.webm?t=1755691617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/95a087c66e4da335130ad6f3d6f1a3d4.mp4?t=1755691617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Toss enemies with your might</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/02aeaad502834c28a9f48bed6500aff2.poster.avif?t=1755691617\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/02aeaad502834c28a9f48bed6500aff2.webm?t=1755691617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/02aeaad502834c28a9f48bed6500aff2.mp4?t=1755691617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Feel the impact of your magic, with physics to throw and smash enemies</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Face powerful foes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dash between your enemies in this first person spell-slinger, featuring a variety of enemies that you will have to overcome in unique ways. Summon them to fight for you, copy their spells or craft more powerful versions of your own.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/99cebdf1c582152e4919454857e91a96.poster.avif?t=1755691617\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/99cebdf1c582152e4919454857e91a96.webm?t=1755691617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277940/extras/99cebdf1c582152e4919454857e91a96.mp4?t=1755691617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bring a friend</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer the world together with PVE and show off your ingenuity with your spells</p>",
